These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, scooter, car, snowmobile
1. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person driving the van is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | van | scooter | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, card-games, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | chess | gardening | collecting | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, chef, freelancer, manager
1. the chef is on the right of the freelancer##1
2. the chef is on the far left or far right##3
3. the software-developer is the software-developer##1
4. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | manager | software-developer | freelancer | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, chess, board-games, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | chess | board-games | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, western, time-travel, drama
1. the person watching western movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | western | drama | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, board-games, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | card-games | board-games | filmmaking |

