1. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the pakistani##5
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
3. the pakistani is between the egyptian and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian | pakistani | canadian |

