3. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | ferret | mouse | horse | turtle |

